These are Puzzles for 6x4 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 6x4-Level-2-1::.
4 different games are played: chess, canasta, go, billiard
There 4 different types of food: broccoli, peach, plum, radish
The people have 4 different hobbies: fishing, gardening, puzzles, writing
The people have 4 different jobs:  entrepreneur, journalist, manager, billiardcher
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: classical, dubstep, funk, r&b
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: family, spy, fantasy, thriller
 1. the billiardcher is on the far right##1
 2. the person playing go is the fan of classical##1
 3. the fan of dubstep is on the left of the fan of funk##1
 4. the person eating plum is on the left of the person eating peach##1
 5. the person playing billiard is the person eating radish##1
 6. the person playing canasta is on the left of the person who's hobby is puzzles##1
 7. the manager is between the person watching family movies and the fan of r&b##2
 8. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the right of the person watching thriller movies##1
 9. the fan of classical is on the right of the entrepreneur##1
10. the person watching family movies is between the manager and the person eating radish##2
11. the person eating broccoli is on the right of the person watching spy movies##1
12. the billiardcher is the person who's hobby is writing##1
13. the fan of funk is between the fan of dubstep and the person who's hobby is puzzles##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2       |     3     |      4      |
| Game      | billiard        | canasta       | go  | chess |
| Food          | radish     | plum         | peach     | broccoli    |
| Hobby         | gardening  | fishing      | puzzles   | writing     |
| Job           | journalist | entrepreneur | manager   | billiardcher     |
| Music-Genre   | dubstep    | funk         | classical | r&b         |
| Movie-Genre         | thriller     | family     | spy  | fantasy       |

