.:: Puzzle 6x4-Level-2-2::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, fanta, soy-milk, sprite
The people have 4 different hobbies: chess, filmmaking, skydiving, writing
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: action, thriller, time-travel, western
There 4 different types of food: plum, pineapple, strawberry, orange
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: davidoff, baccarat, chaman, old-henry
The people use 4 different means of transport: bike, bus, ship, train
 1. the baccarat-smoker is between the person who's hobby is skydiving and the person driving the bike##2
 2. the old-henry-smoker is on the left of the person watching time-travel movies##1
 3. the person who's hobby is writing is on the left of the davidoff-smoker##1
 4. the baccarat-smoker is between the person drinking almond-milk and the person driving the ship##2
 5. the person eating plum is the person drinking fanta##1
 6. the person eating strawberry is on the far right##1
 7. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the right of the person eating pineapple##1
 8. the person driving the ship is between the person watching action movies and the person who's hobby is writing##2
 9. the person watching thriller movies is the person who's hobby is writing##1
10. the person who's hobby is chess is on the far left##1
11. the person eating plum is the person watching time-travel movies##1
12. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1
13. the chaman-smoker is on the right of the person driving the bus##1
14. the person drinking fanta is on the left of the baccarat-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |     3      |      4      |
| Beverage      | sprite    | fanta       | soy-milk   | almond-milk |
