 7. the person driving the van is between the person who's birthday is in november and the person drinking tea##2
 8. the person drinking hot-chocolate is the fan of hip-hop##1
 9. the person drinking 7up is between the person driving the van and the fan of trance##2
10. the person who's sport is soccer is on the left of the person who's sport is handball##1
11. the person drinking tea is the person driving the subway##1
12. the person eating lime is the person driving the skateboard##1
13. the fan of gospel is between the person eating cauliflower and the person who's birthday is in september##2

