.:: Puzzle 6x4-Level-2-15::.
House: palace, cape-cod, futuristic, craftsman
There 4 different types of food: blueberry, radish, strawberry, zucchini
The people use 4 different means of transport: bike, snowmobile, airplane, train
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: ambient, pop, salsa, soul
There are 4 different nationalities: american, british, dutch, german
4 different pets are kept: frog, mouse, rat, turtle
 1. the person eating blueberry is on the right of the american##1
 2. the dutch is on the left of the owner of the frog##1
 3. the owner of the mouse is on the far left##1
 4. the palace house is on the left of the person driving the airplane##1
 5. the owner of the rat is on the far right##1
 6. the fan of soul is between the person driving the bike and the person eating zucchini##2
 7. the german is on the left of the fan of ambient##1
 8. the craftsman house is on the far left##1
 9. the german is the person eating blueberry##1
10. the person driving the snowmobile is the owner of the turtle##1
11. the fan of salsa is on the right of the person eating strawberry##1
12. the cape-cod house is the owner of the rat##1
13. the fan of salsa is on the right of the person driving the train##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |    2     |      3      |    4     |
| House      | craftsman        | futuristic     | palace        | cape-cod    |
| Food          | strawberry     | radish   | blueberry   | zucchini |
| Transport           | train | bike  | snowmobile | airplane |
| Music-Genre   | pop            | salsa    | soul        | ambient  |
| Nationality   | dutch          | american | german      | british  |
| Pet           | mouse          | frog     | turtle      | rat      |

