.:: Puzzle 6x4-Level-2-16::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: 7up, almond-milk, coffee, milk
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: prince, bluemaster, oliveros, davidoff
The people have 4 different jobs:  analyst, chef, electrician, manager
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: documentary, musical, satire, thriller
There are 4 different nationalities: brazilian, french, german, indian
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: pop, salsa, gospel, r&b
 1. the fan of gospel is the bluemaster-smoker##1
 2. the fan of r&b is on the right of the person drinking coffee##1
 3. the person drinking almond-milk is the indian##1
 4. the fan of r&b is on the left of the analyst##1
 5. the person drinking milk is on the left of the french##1
 6. the person watching satire movies is on the right of the person watching documentary movies##1
 7. the person drinking coffee is between the electrician and the davidoff-smoker##2
 8. the electrician is the german##1
 9. the person watching thriller movies is between the fan of r&b and the german##2
10. the fan of r&b is on the left of the bluemaster-smoker##1
11. the manager is on the left of the davidoff-smoker##1
12. the fan of salsa is on the left of the person drinking almond-milk##1
13. the oliveros-smoker is the fan of pop##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |      2      |      3      |     4     |
| Beverage      | milk        | coffee      | almond-milk | 7up       |
| Cigar         | oliveros | prince | davidoff   | bluemaster   |
| Job           | electrician | manager     | chef        | analyst   |
| Movie-Genre   | musical     | thriller    | documentary | satire    |
| Nationality   | german      | french      | indian      | brazilian |
| Music-Genre           | pop      | salsa    | r&b       | gospel  |

