.:: Puzzle 6x4-Level-2-17::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, lemonade, mirinda, tea
There 4 different types of food: blueberry, carrot, kale, kiwi
The people have 4 different jobs:  chef, freelancer, pilot, security-guard
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: funk, gospel, metal, reggae
City: hamburg, marseilles, san-francisco, venice
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: handball, tennis, basketball, volleyball
 1. the person who's sport is tennis is on the right of the fan of gospel##1
 2. the person eating carrot is on the left of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
 3. the person who's sport is handball is on the left of the pilot##1
 4. the person who's sport is basketball is on the left of the person drinking lemonade##1
 5. the chef is on the left of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
 6. the person eating blueberry is on the right of the person eating kiwi##1
 7. the fan of reggae is on the left of the person who's sport is basketball##1
 8. the person eating kiwi is between the person traveling to hamburg and the person who's sport is tennis##2
 9. the person drinking tea is on the far left##1
10. the person traveling to venice is on the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
11. the person who's sport is handball is the security-guard##1
12. the person drinking mirinda is on the far right##1
13. the fan of funk is between the chef and the person who's sport is handball##2
14. the security-guard is on the left of the person traveling to san-francisco##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |       2       |       3        |     4     |
| Beverage      | tea      | hot-chocolate | lemonade       | mirinda   |
| Food          | carrot   | kale          | kiwi           | blueberry |
| Job           | chef     | freelancer    | security-guard | pilot     |
| Music-Genre   | reggae   | funk          | gospel         | metal     |
| City   | marseilles    | hamburg      | venice       | san-francisco    |
| Sport           | volleyball | basketball       | handball         | tennis  |

