.:: Puzzle 6x4-Level-2-18::.
There 4 different types of food: artichoke, peach, pear, radish
House: wooden, modern, futuristic, victorian
4 different games are played: scrabble, go, snooker, billiard
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: crime, disaster, satire, time-travel
There are 4 different nationalities: australian, british, italian, turkish
The people use 4 different means of transport: car, snowmobile, train, trike
 1. the person eating artichoke is on the right of the person playing snooker##1
 2. the person watching satire movies is between the person playing billiard and the person playing scrabble##2
 3. the person eating pear is on the right of the person eating radish##1
 4. the person watching time-travel movies is on the right of the person playing go##1
 5. the person driving the car is on the right of the australian##1
 6. the modern house is between the person driving the car and the british##2
 7. the person driving the trike is between the australian and the person driving the snowmobile##2
 8. the person driving the car is on the right of the person eating peach##1
 9. the futuristic house is on the right of the person watching disaster movies##1
10. the futuristic house is the person playing billiard##1
11. the person playing go is on the left of the british##1
12. the wooden house is on the left of the person driving the trike##1
13. the italian is the person eating artichoke##1
14. the modern house is the modern house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |       3       |      4      |
| Food          | radish     | pear        | peach         | artichoke   |
| House         | wooden     | futuristic     | modern    | victorian |
| Game           | go  | billiard      | snooker | scrabble   |
| Movie-Genre   | disaster   | time-travel | satire        | crime       |
| Nationality   | turkish    | british     | australian    | italian     |
| Transport     | snowmobile | trike       | train         | car         |

